    • getCommand

      public static dev.jorel.commandapi.CommandAPICommand getCommand()
      Creates the /wiki config <get|reload|set> subcommand.

      Permission: wikicraft.command.config

      Usage: /wiki config <get|reload|set>

      • /wiki config get [key]: Gets a config value
      • /wiki config reload: Reloads the config.yml file
      • /wiki config set <key> [value]: Sets a config value
      Returns:
      A CommandAPICommand object representing the /wiki config subcommand
